          "type": "text",
          "text": "1. Overview"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The stored procedure "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "[Billing].[usp_BWT_Billing_Request]",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " is designed to retrieve billing information for specific accounts during a specified billing period. It extracts and formats data from the "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Billing.uvw_BWT_Billing_Request",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " view, focusing on energy usage, demand, charges, and taxes. The procedure filters results based on a given billing period and a predefined list of account numbers, then orders the results by billing period and account number."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
