    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The procedure involves multiple data transformations, including string manipulation, type casting, and conditional logic. It also includes a specific filtering mechanism and ordering, which adds to its complexity. However, it does not involve complex joins, subqueries, or dynamic SQL, keeping it at a medium complexity level."
        }
